powerbar is a multi socket with a network interface. The sockets are switchable
using 

Compiling the code:
===================
mkdir _build
cd _build
cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../powerbar/toolchain-avr-gcc.cmake  ../powerbar

Fuse bits:
====================================
low fuse:  0xef
high fuse: 0xd9

Common lantronix device settings:
=================================

Configurable Pins:
    CP1: Modem Control Out

Connection:
    Disconnect Mode: on DTR 

